      ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.                                    
      DATA DIVISION.                                           
      WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.                                 
    77 WS-NAME PIC X(20).                                      
    77 WS-ROLLNO  PIC X(20).                                   
       77 WS-CNT  PIC 9(1).                             
     PROCEDURE DIVISION.                            
         ACCEPT  WS-CNT.                            
         PERFORM 100-INPUT-PARA UNTIL WS-CNT = 0.   
           STOP RUN.                                
   100-INPUT-PARA.                                  
         ACCEPT  WS-ROLLNO.                         
         ACCEPT  WS-NAME.                           
         DISPLAY WS-ROLLNO.                         
         DISPLAY WS-NAME.                           
         SUBTRACT 1 FROM WS-CNT.                    
